  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69dedd464962039994648252",
      "text": "誰かにとって不快かもしれない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776213325,
      "updated": 1776213325
    },
    {
      "id": "69dedd4c00000000003ceb2e",
      "text": "不快に思う人はいる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776213325,
      "updated": 1776213340
    },
    {
      "id": "69dedd4d00000000003ceb2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776213326,
      "updated": 1776213326
    },
    {
      "id": "69df06e3000000000059aa79",
      "text": "[Scrapboxの利用規約]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776223971,
      "updated": 1776223980
    },
    {
      "id": "69df06ef000000000059aa7a",
      "text": "> (13) 弊社、本サービスの他の利用者またはその他の第三者に不利益、損害、不快感を与える行為",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776223983,
      "updated": 1776224034
    },
    {
      "id": "69df072300000000003ceb37",
      "text": "不快感を与える行為はやってはいけない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776224035,
      "updated": 1776224103
    },
    {
      "id": "69df075400000000003ceb38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776224084,
      "updated": 1776224084
    },
    {
      "id": "69dedd9400000000003ceb30",
      "text": "[嫌なことを表明するのが良いという文化]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776213397,
      "updated": 1776213406
